data.description: Experience the practicality and charm of condo living in this 3-bedroom, 2-bath unit with a 1-car attached garage abode. Situated on the first floor for easy access, this condo unit boasts an open floor plan that creates a welcoming and spacious ambiance. Nestled in the sought-after community of Windsor Falls, you'll enjoy the best of comfort and convenience. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by 10' ceilings and neutral finishes throughout, providing a canvas for your personal style. The kitchen is fitted with stainless steel appliances, extra-tall cabinets, and an abundance of storage space for all your daily culinary needs. The owner's suite is a tranquil retreat, featuring a convenient walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with a soaking tub and a separate shower. Nestled within a gated community, you'll have access to full amenities including a swimming pool, fitness center, and a playground, ensuring that there's always something to do. With it's prime location, you'll enjoy easy access to St. Johns Town Center, Jacksonville Beach, and major conveniences. Don't miss the opportunity to live the condo lifestyle at it's finest.
